<h2>Dominic Widdows Essay Page</h2>

Nobody writes essays nowadays, everyone writes blogs. I tried to write
a blog for a few years, but the problem was that I just can't write
blogs. They keep turning back into essays. So I gave up and am going
to start writing essays again and just putting them on the web. The
upside is that I can format them and organize them as I see fit,
rather than presume that chronology is the main organizing
principle. The main downside is that you can't post comments directly,
though with comment spam on the up, this wasn't useful any more. If
you want to comment on any of these essays, it shouldn't be hard to
figure out how to contact me.

